name: Instantâneos em Movimento (Moving Snapshots) - Aves: #4 Vanellus chilensis
description: The fourth piece in the Moving Snapshots collection features Vanellus chilensis (also known as "Quero-quero", "quem-quem", "espanta-boiada", "tetéu" e "xexéu"). This piece was created from a photograph that we make available for free in stock images websites and, therefore, we want to inherit the gratuity of the original photo for this animation. Collect this artwork and, if you want, contact us to receive the link to download the original image. http://primeiraprova.com
